mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#19150F">In particular, LIHEAP seeks to make home energy more affordable for two groups of low income households that have the highest home energy needs:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">
        <![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:
